Going for a holiday? ⛺️Looking for a new experience? ⛰️Save this for later ✨ @breatheresortsandvillas in Chikmagalur can be one of the best picks for your next weekend getaway/staycation 🐩🌅⛰️🏕️🛀 

Glamping derived from the words ‘Glamorous’ and ‘Camping’ is an outdoor escape that combines the closeness to nature associated with camping with the luxury and convenience of proper self-catered accommodation. 🌳🌴🌳

Details : 

🔺4 hour drive from Bangalore, 
nestled in Chikmagalur overlooking the beautiful Mullayangiri Peak, this property exhales luxury! 

🔺Each glamp has an exclusive deck with a jacuzzi and an outdoor shower with incredible views 

🔺10+ acres of landscaped greenery amidst coffee estates and exotic jungle trees 

🔺Pet friendly, their mascot is a husky and you can find plenty of them running around 🥹🐩

🔺Rejuvenate your body and mind through yoga sessions and personalised spa experiences. 

There’s a lot more to do on the property. Please reach out to me if you need any more information 🐩⛰️🌻

grwm in Vietnam 🇻🇳☀️ Xin chao 

Hey from Hoi An 🌱🏮
Starting the day with one of my favorite combos—white linen trousers, a brown linen shirt, and this Vietnamese hat that I absolutely love.
It’s lightweight, comfy, and perfect for the heat here.
I’m heading out to this spot called Café Slow. I’ve heard so much about it—hidden in a quiet lane, super aesthetic, and yeah... the coffee?  It’s amazing🤌🏻
So if you’re into slow mornings, beautiful spaces, and soaking in the local vibe—this one’s for you.
